name: Isabella_Modern_Free_Form_Wood_2-piece_Coffee_Table_Set
reviews: I ordered this coffee table and it was missing instructions and parts. It's been 2 months and still no replacement parts..
Cute design, look like the pics, but a little lower to the ground than I expected but no complaints
Nice but feels a little cheap - so was the price so I can't complain.
description:
These Free-Form Coffee tables are suitable for any modern setting
with their retro style. Three legged supports and smooth finished
tops provide a stylish look for living spaces. The smaller table
can even be fit under the large one to save space.
